## GitHub仓库设置

创建仓库时填写：

| 字段 | 内容 |
|------|------|
| **Repository name** | `shixintong-credit-scoring` |
| **Description** | Multi-source data fusion credit scoring system for small catering enterprises based on XGBoost |
| **Public/Private** | Public（评委才能看到） |
| **Add .gitignore** | Python |
| **Choose a license** | MIT |

